        "creatureType": "",
        "details": {
            "description": "<p>A pile of dust and bone meal, several inches deep and 10 feet across on each side, blocks the tunnel to the surface. It is suffused with the despair of the slowly dying, and summons vengeful skeletal hands to hunt down anyone who dares attempt to leave the area.</p>",
            "disable": "<p><span data-pf2-check=\"religion\" data-pf2-traits=\"haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"Administer Burial Rites DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"15\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Religion</span> (trained) to speak the proper burial rites, <span data-pf2-check=\"occultism\" data-pf2-traits=\"haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"Exorcise Spirits DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"15\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Occultism</span> (trained) to exorcise the lingering souls, or <span data-pf2-check=\"intimidation\" data-pf2-traits=\"haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"Scare Away Spirits DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"17\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Intimidation</span> to scare the fearful souls away.</p>\n<p>These actions have the verbal trait. Each check to disable the hazard requires 2 actions, and two total successes are required to disable the haunt.</p>",
            "isComplex": true,
            "level": {
                "value": 1
            },
            "reset": "<p>The haunt deactivates if no creatures remain within 30 feet but resets immediately thereafter unless disabled. If tthe haunt is disabled, it resets after 24 hours.</p>",
            "routine": "<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> Spectral hands grasp at creatures in the area. Each creature within 30 feet of the dust pile takes [[/r 1d4 #negative]]{1d4 negative damage} (<span data-pf2-check=\"will\" data-pf2-traits=\"haunt\" data-pf2-label=\"Grasping Hands DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"17\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Will</span> save<span data-visibility=\"gm\">; creatures that critically fail this saving throw are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 1 round</span>).</p>"
        },
